text: Reunited is a 2014 album by the family group The Jets, at this point composed of siblings Eddie, Elizabeth, Haini, Kathi, Leroy, Moana, Natalia and Rudy Wolfgramm. It features six new songs and four re-recordings of past hit songs. ==Track listing== # "Cross My Broken Heart" # "Make It Real" # "Pass Me By" # "So Cool" # "Take My Hand" # "Crush on You" # "You Got It All" # "Pride" # "Believe in Love" # "Don't" Category:2014 albums Category:The Jets (band) albums
